<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Drawing Q without a U is every Scrabble player's nightmare — unless you know the Q-without-U words. Q is worth 10 points (the highest single-tile value alongside Z), and these special words let you deploy it without waiting for a U. Memorize them and the Q becomes an asset, not a burden.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why Q-Without-U Words Matter</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
