    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">-10</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Penalty if stuck at end</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>If you're stuck with Q at game end, you lose 10 points. Knowing these words transforms Q from a liability into a premium scoring tile that you can deploy on almost any turn.</p>

